title.rendered: Taj777 News is the associate sponsor of Salem Spartans in TNPL 2022

content.rendered:
From the time T20 format has come into play, with IPL and similar looking events has made the T20 format even more crazier than before. And why not, when people are ready to embrace the format with open arms.

As IPL has taken-off since 2008, there are many other regional leagues for instance the Tamil Nadu Cricket league which has also been active since 2016 to boost up the domestic cricket with its talent. Tamil Nadu Cricket league (TNPL) was inaugurated by MS Dhoni.

For an update, one of the eight teams from TNPL, Salem Spartans has added a bunch of sponsors to its team in order to have a fruitful season. One of the latest that the franchise Salem Spartans have added to their list is the Taj777news as their associate sponsor. Taj777News will be responsible to showcase all the latest updates coming from the franchise in the form of videos, commentary, news and so on.

As an additive, the Taj777news through its digital app platform will also be showcasing articles and coverages consisting with useful stats & ranking of your favourite team and player. However, as we spoke about the bunch of sponsors, the list continues further. Vision11, India’s another fastest growing fantasy platform with 5M users has been declared the associate sponsor for Salem Spartan which is India’s biggest sport gaming platform. Under this app you can get all the sport details as well as the user can create his/her own team of real-life players from the upcoming matches, field performances, score points and so on.

In the list, Freyer International is another sponsor that Salem Spartans has added to its team as logistics partner. Freyer International as a sponsor will be responsible to provide solutions related to international forwarding, logistics and the entire supply chain management.

With eight teams, Tamil Nadu Cricket League in its sixth edition of this season (2022) is going to commence its most awaited league of year from June 23rd lasting till 31st July, 2022. Cricket Format will be T20.

Salem Spartan Playing XI squad (2022)

Darryl Ferrario (Captain), Vijay Shankar, Murugan Ashwin, Akshay Srinivasan, S Abhishek, Vijay Shankar, M Ganesh Moorthi, S Boopalan, Umashankar Sushil, Ravi Karthikeyan, Lokesh Raj, Gopinath, G Periyaswamy, B Praneesh, A Aarif, AVR Rathnam, G Kishoor, M Suganesh, Abhinav Vishnu, Shubham Mehta, M Vijay Kumar, Rajendran Karthikeyan, Shubham Mehta
